{
  "chapter": 1,
  "chapter_summary": "本章讲述了一起重大的镖银失踪案。一百零三名武林好手护送价值三千五百万两的金珠珍宝，在太行山下小镇神秘失踪，唯一生还者崔诚身负重伤。中原大侠熊天健、名医叶星士、十二连环坞总瓢把子鹰眼老七等保人组成搜索队，将崔诚安置在十二连环坞的密室中。然而崔诚、程中和萧红珠三人在严密防守下被一柄极薄的快刀杀死。太平王世子限期四十天追回镖银。众人商议后兵分三路：熊天健回太行山调查，叶星士追查善使刀的高手，王毅筹款。鹰眼老七决定寻找陆小凤相助，但赶到卧云楼时发现陆小凤已出海，只得失望而归。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_tian_jian",
      "speaker_name": "熊天健",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们是在当地一家客栈的坑洞里找到他的，当时他已晕迷不醒，奄奄一息。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_num": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xing_shi",
      "speaker_name": "叶星士",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他身上共有刀伤六处，虽然因为流血过多而晕迷，幸好伤不在要害，只要找个安全的地方让他静养三五天，我保证他一定恢复清醒。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_num": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_yan_lao_qi",
      "speaker_name": "鹰眼老七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在他已被送到一个绝对安全的地方休养，不经我们全体同意，连一只苍蝇都飞不进去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_num": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "程寨主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他昨天晚上已醒过一次，还喝了半碗参汤，解了一次手，等我们替他换过药后，他才睡着的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_num": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_yan_lao_qi",
      "speaker_name": "鹰眼老七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他解出的粪便中已没有血丝，今天早上已经能开口要水喝，还看着我笑了笑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_num": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_yan_lao_qi",
      "speaker_name": "鹰眼老七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你说得不错，这地方实在连只苍蝇都飞不进去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_num": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xing_shi",
      "speaker_name": "叶星士",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他们死了至少已有一个半时辰，是被一柄锋刃极薄的快刀杀死的，一刀就已致命！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_num": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xing_shi",
      "speaker_name": "叶星士",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为刀的锋刃太薄，出手太快，所以连伤口都没有留下。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_num": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xing_shi",
      "speaker_name": "叶星士",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "致命的刀伤无疑在肺叶下端。一刀刺入，血液立刻大量涌入胸腔，所以没有血流出来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_num": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "防守人员",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在这两个时辰中，除了萧夫人和程寨主，绝没有第三个人出入过。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_num": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tai_ping_wang_shi_zi",
      "speaker_name": "太平王的世子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "照你这么说，除非他是个隐形的人！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_num": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_yan_lao_qi",
      "speaker_name": "鹰眼老七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "凶手是怎么进去的？这世上当然绝没有真能隐形的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_num": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tai_ping_wang_shi_zi",
      "speaker_name": "太平王的世子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我可以给你们四十天的限期，让你们去把这批珠宝追回来，否则……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_num": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xing_shi",
      "speaker_name": "叶星士",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这已不是第一次。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_num": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xing_shi",
      "speaker_name": "叶星士",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "上个月底长江水上飞，在作每日例行的巡查时，忽然暴毙在水中，我也曾被他们帮中的子弟请去鉴定他的死因。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_num": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_tian_jian",
      "speaker_name": "熊天健",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他的死因也跟崔诚一样？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_num": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xing_shi",
      "speaker_name": "叶星士",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他身上也完全没有伤痕血迹，我整整花了三天功夫，才查出他内腑肺叶下的刀伤，也同样是一刀就已致命！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_num": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_tian_jian",
      "speaker_name": "熊天健",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他是在水中被刺的了？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_num": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xing_shi",
      "speaker_name": "叶星士",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_num": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_tian_jian",
      "speaker_name": "熊天健",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我也想起了一件事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_num": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi",
      "speaker_name": "王毅",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_num": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_tian_jian",
      "speaker_name": "熊天健",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "今年年初，嵩阳‘铁剑山庄’的老庄主在他的藏剑阁中练剑时，忽然暴毙，至今还没有人知道他的死因。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_num": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_tian_jian",
      "speaker_name": "熊天健",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在我才想到，他很可能也是被同一个刺客暗杀的！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_num": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xing_shi",
      "speaker_name": "叶星士",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他当真是在练剑时被刺的，这刺客的刀就未免太可怕了。",
      "tone": "皱眉",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_num": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_yan_lao_qi",
      "speaker_name": "鹰眼老七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么我们是不是就应该坐在这里，等着他来将我们一个个杀光！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_num": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_yan_lao_qi",
      "speaker_name": "鹰眼老七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就算这刺客真的有三头六臂，真的会隐形，我也要把他找出来！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_num": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "某人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你准备到哪里去？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_num": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_yan_lao_qi",
      "speaker_name": "鹰眼老七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我去找陆小凤。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_num": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "某人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就是那个有四条眉毛的陆小凤？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_num": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_yan_lao_qi",
      "speaker_name": "鹰眼老七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "假如世上还有人能替我们找出那凶手来，一定就是陆小凤。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_num": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "某人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "据说这个人是个浪子，浪迹天涯，四海为家，你准备到哪里去找他？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_num": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_yan_lao_qi",
      "speaker_name": "鹰眼老七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哪里的粽子做得最好，我就到哪里去找。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_num": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_yan_lao_qi",
      "speaker_name": "鹰眼老七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我正准备到那里去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_num": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_yan_lao_qi",
      "speaker_name": "鹰眼老七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "卧云楼主人一向好客，端阳才过三天，他一定不会放陆小凤走的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_num": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_yun_lou_zhu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卧云楼主人",
      "listener": "char_ying_yan_lao_qi",
      "text": "陆小凤来过，几乎每年端午前后他都要来住几天。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_num": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_yun_lou_zhu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卧云楼主人",
      "listener": "char_ying_yan_lao_qi",
      "text": "这就是我特地为他挑选的竹叶青，你尝尝怎么样？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_num": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_yun_lou_zhu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卧云楼主人",
      "listener": "char_ying_yan_lao_qi",
      "text": "现在他的人呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_num": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_yun_lou_zhu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卧云楼主人",
      "listener": "char_ying_yan_lao_qi",
      "text": "今年他的兴致好像不如往年，总显得有点心事重重，连这坛酒都没有喝完，就一定要走，连我都留不住！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_num": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_yan_lao_qi",
      "speaker_name": "鹰眼老七",
      "listener": "char_wu_yun_lou_zhu_ren",
      "text": "他太喜欢管闲事，什么事都管，不该管的也要管，却忘了替自己打算打算，一个人到了三十岁还没有成家，心情怎么会好得起来？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_num": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_yan_lao_qi",
      "speaker_name": "鹰眼老七",
      "listener": "char_wu_yun_lou_zhu_ren",
      "text": "你知不知道他会到什么地方去？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_num": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_yun_lou_zhu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卧云楼主人",
      "listener": "char_ying_yan_lao_qi",
      "text": "我好像听他说过，他要到海外去散散心。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_num": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_yun_lou_zhu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卧云楼主人",
      "listener": "char_ying_yan_lao_qi",
      "text": "你是说他要出海去？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_num": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_yun_lou_zhu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卧云楼主人",
      "listener": "char_ying_yan_lao_qi",
      "text": "现在他想必已到了海上。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_num": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_yan_lao_qi",
      "speaker_name": "鹰眼老七",
      "listener": "char_wu_yun_lou_zhu_ren",
      "text": "他秋深的时候就会回来的，一定还会到我这里吃月饼，你有什么事，我可以转告他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_num": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_yan_lao_qi",
      "speaker_name": "鹰眼老七",
      "listener": "char_wu_yun_lou_zhu_ren",
      "text": "到了那时候，我只有一件事找他做了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_num": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_yun_lou_zhu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卧云楼主人",
      "listener": "char_ying_yan_lao_qi",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_num": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_yan_lao_qi",
      "speaker_name": "鹰眼老七",
      "listener": "char_wu_yun_lou_zhu_ren",
      "text": "找他去抬棺材。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_num": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_yun_lou_zhu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卧云楼主人",
      "listener": "char_ying_yan_lao_qi",
      "text": "谁的？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_num": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_yan_lao_qi",
      "speaker_name": "鹰眼老七",
      "listener": "char_wu_yun_lou_zhu_ren",
      "text": "我的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_num": 250
    }
  ],
